text: Bianca Sandu (born 22 April 1992) is a Romanian footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Romania women's national team. ==Career== Sandu has been capped for the Romania national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian women's footballers Category:Romania women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders
